00:01:58.820 --> 00:02:00.200
To make it easy to read

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:02.000
Then I will abbreviate it as below

00:02:02.000 --> 00:02:03.460
It's called a CC strategy

00:02:03.460 --> 00:02:05.180
CC strategy is simply a matter of fact

00:02:05.180 --> 00:02:06.740
You buy a bunch of stocks first

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:11.040
Then sell the call option on the stock

00:02:11.040 --> 00:02:14.100
It is equivalent to your right to sell a stock to rise

00:02:14.100 --> 00:02:15.800
This way you can collect royalties

00:02:15.800 --> 00:02:18.040
Royalties are CC policy

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:20.080
The main source of income

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:21.380
But this strategy

00:02:21.380 --> 00:02:23.120
There are some obvious flaws

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:24.160
First

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.000
The Nature of CC Strategy

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.160
is bearish

00:02:27.160 --> 00:02:28.840
Because it's a sell-bullish sell

00:02:28.840 --> 00:02:31.840
Sell the right to rise to others

00:02:31.840 --> 00:02:34.180
Then if at the stipulated time

00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:37.900
The share price rises to the price specified in the contract

00:02:37.900 --> 00:02:40.820
Then the fund must sell the shares

00:02:40.820 --> 00:02:42.440
If the condition is not met

00:02:42.440 --> 00:02:44.320
Then the fund can keep shares

00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:45.480
But anyway

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:48.660
This strategy can also make a lot of money

00:02:48.660 --> 00:02:50.020
But there is a problem here

00:02:50.020 --> 00:02:50.720
That is to say

00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:53.200
The rising stock market environment

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:56.280
It is very detrimental to the CC strategy

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:58.140
Then the stock price continues to rise

00:02:58.140 --> 00:03:01.240
Then the CC strategy has to continue to sell stocks

00:03:01.860 --> 00:03:03.980
Thus making the whole net worth

00:03:03.980 --> 00:03:05.180
In a gradual reduction

00:03:05.180 --> 00:03:08.040
But the market continues to fall

00:03:08.040 --> 00:03:09.500
For CC Strategy

